Yaduwar cututtukan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan adadin cututtukan coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan canjin a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya wanda ya tabbatar da hakan, yayin da a matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 ta duniya tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga gogewar da aka samu a Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da sassan gaggawa suna bukatar kara shirye-shiryen su na biye da marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawar lafiya, musamman gaggawa.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2020, an samu rahoton wasu mutane da suka kamu da cutar sankara a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
Ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar ta kasar Sin ta bayyana dalilin sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira ciwon huhu mai tsanani na alamun cutar coronavirus 2 ((SARS-CoV-2).
Har zuwa yanzu, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Akwai hujja har zuwa 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, kamar kumburi na numfashi a cikin marasa lafiya ko rashin burburin, kuma galibi suna warkewa.
A kusan kashi 14% na lokuta, COVID-19 yana haifar da ciwo mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar magani yayin da sauran kashi 6% na lokuta suna magance ciwo mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar kulawa da gaggawa.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya masu magani na COVID-19 kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta canje-canje a cikin duk abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU / EEA) da Burtaniya (UK) idan aka kwatanta da lardin Hubei. China.
Hakanan muna kwatanta adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai EU / EEA da Burtaniya UK da Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Maganganun COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai EU / EEA da Burtaniya UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ta bazu zuwa wurare da yawa a yanayin ƙasa. Saurin cutar ta COVID-19 a sauran duniya yanzu yayi kama da na wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta amince da COVID-19 a matsayin cuta ta duniya.
A ranar 5 ga watan Maris na shekarar 2020, a cikin taron Eurosurveilance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon shari'ar COVID-19 a Turai kamar yadda Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta WHO ta bayyana.
A cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai EU/EEA, an bayar da rahoton mutum uku na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an lura da shari'o'in COVID-19 na farko a duk ƙasashe 30 na Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai EU / EEA da Burtaniya (UK), yayin da tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da wannan kwanan wata, an ba da rahoton shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun cikakken adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da kuma yawan abubuwan da suka faru
Cibiyar Tarayya da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), yawan adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka bayyana a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samu daga tushe na hukuma kawai kamar ma'aikatun lafiya na tarayya, shugabannin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya WHO, ana sanar da su kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanin don kimanta canjin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta shi da na Italiya.
A matsayinmu na shugaban rahoto kan shari'o'in COVID-19, mun lissafa kwanaki 14 na rage yawan abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19, don haka muna lissafin yanayin COVID-19 na halitta a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya, tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun gabatar da jimlar adadin wadanda aka gano a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Canjin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Canje-canje daga 14 na yau da kullum na rage yawan lokuta na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya suna faruwa gaba ɗaya a cikin Hubei (China) (zane 1).
A cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya, yawan adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu kuma yanzu ya ƙaru da sauri a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Shayin tallafi).
Wannan ya faru ne saboda yaduwar yawan shari'o'in da aka bayyana a Italiya, amma duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya suna nuna karuwa a yawan adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 (Shayin da aka taimaka).
Shafin 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin shari'o'in COVID-19, a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU / EEA da Burtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton jimlar adadin shari'o'in da za a iya kwatanta da na Italiya makonni 2 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka gano suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Canjin da aka lura a cikin yawan abubuwan da ke faruwa na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar ta yadu a duniya a cikin saurin da za a iya kwatanta da kowace ƙasa.
Wannan ya zo ne saboda ƙasashe suna da bambancin matakan, bambancin amsa ga lafiyar jama'a a cikin ƙasa, da yiwuwar ƙayyade shari'o'i daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da kuma abubuwan da za a yi la'akari da su don zaɓin marasa lafiya da za a bincika don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin daidaitawa.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke dauke da COVID-19 ke bukatar sashen kula da gaggawa yayin da kafofin yada labarai suka ruwaito cewa asibitoci da kayan aikin kula da yankin sun kai matakin da suka fi dacewa.
Bayanai na rajistar shari'o'in COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko a sashen kula da gaggawa cewa a halin yanzu ana samun su ne a matakin EU/EEU kawai a kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in, bi da bi (ba a bayyana bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara shi a cikin tsari don canja bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
Wani binciken da aka gudanar a shekarar 2010-11 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin samun kulawa ta gaggawa da kuma gadajen kulawa ta tsakiya a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kowace mutane 100,000 a cikin al'ummar Burtuga.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun kuɗi fiye da ko ƙasa da na Italiya (12.5 a cikin gaggawa da kuma gadaje na gaggawa na 100,000 a kowace mutum a cikin al'umma a shekarar 2010-11)
A cikin matakan tsarawa game da haɗa nauyin kula da lafiya, tare da ƙididdigar kowane ƙasar EU / EEA da Burtaniya don fifita yanayin COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti dangane da > 90% haɗarin wuce haddi na yawan gado na gaggawa, an nuna shi a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na ECDC don kimanta haɗarin gaggawa na COVID-19.
Tun da yawan shari'o'i yana ƙaruwa a wasu yankuna na ƙasashen EU/EEA da na Burtaniya, da kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin gaggawa waɗanda yawanci ke aiki don daidaitawa da al'umma a cikin yankuna, ya kamata a sa bayanai game da shari'o'i da gadon gaggawa a cikin wuraren da ake samun su a cikin yankin 2 (NUTS-2) matakin.
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma halin yanzu a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 ta duniya tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Kasashe, Asibitoci da sassan gaggawa dole ne su shirya kansu don daidaitawar watsawar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawar likita, musamman kulawar gaggawa, kamar yadda yake faruwa a yankunan da aka shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka ambata a cikin kimanta haɗarin gaggawa na kwanan nan, hanzari, aiki mai mahimmanci yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2, ta hanyar motsawa daga hanyar sarrafawa zuwa ragewa, tare da ƙaruwa mai sauri a cikin adadin shari'o'in da bazai iya ba da shawarar da aka yi wa masu tuki da asibitoci a cikin lokaci ba don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita halayen su daidai idan ba a aiwatar da su ba a gaba.
Ƙididdigar haɗari na gaggawa ta ƙara matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar ta duniya.
Akwai ƙarancin dama ga ƙasashe da ke da damar haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafa su don rage yaduwar SARS-COV-2 da rage matsin lamba akan kiwon lafiya.
Idan wannan ya kasa, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA zai fuskanci ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa ta gaggawa a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ya haifar da cutar ta cutar huhu mai tsanani (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ya kashe mutane sama da 3,000 zuwa yanzu kuma ya shafi sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'in ɗan adam.
Hakanan, irin wannan kwayar cutar, SARS-CoV, wacce ta haifar da SARS ga dubban mutane a cikin 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya wucewa ta hanyar firikwensin kuma ta haifar da alamun bayyanar irin wannan ta hanyar iri ɗaya.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin tashin hankali da mutuwa fiye da SARS amma yana da yawa kuma yana shafar manya fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
A cikin martani ga yawan wallafe-wallafen cututtuka masu tasowa, wannan labarin yana ƙoƙarin kawo cikakken ra'ayi game da batun bincike mai sauƙi.
Muna rufe abubuwan da suka shafi cututtukan cututtuka, asalin cutar, nazarin ƙwayoyin cuta, bincike, magani, tsinkaya na dalilin ciwo, da rigakafin ciwo.
Duk da cewa akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ake bukatar amsoshi, muna fatan wannan ra'ayi zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma kawo karshen cutar.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa gani ba kuma an manta da shi ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka gaya musu cewa suna cikin gidaje a cikin hutu na makonni bayan barkewar sabon cutar.
Kwayar cutar tana kama da cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da mummunan cututtukan huhu na SARS a cikin 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanya masa suna SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ke da alaƙa da ita ta sanya masa suna COVID-19 (Covid-19).
Cutar zazzabin cizon sauro ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a duk fadin kasar da kuma wasu wurare kusan 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da fiye da 80,000 da aka tabbatar da shari'o'in COVID-19, tare da fiye da 40,000 marasa lafiya sun warke kuma fiye da 3,000 marasa lafiya sun mutu.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "abokin gaba na farko na al'umma" ne kuma yana iya zama mafi iko fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin kasa da watanni biyu, an buga takardu sama da 200 game da COVID-19 ciki har da cutar ta kamuwa da cuta, nazarin cutar ta kamuwa da cuta, nazarin asalinta, bincike, da magani tun lokacin da aka fara bayar da rahoton ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 wanda ya nuna jerin yadda aka kamu da cutar a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan edita yana ƙoƙarin taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin sabon yanki na al'ada wanda ke ci gaba cikin sauƙi.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, muna ƙoƙarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da wani cuta da COVID ta haifar, cutar huhu ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, barkewar 2012).
Zan kuma tattauna abin da muka koya zuwa yanzu dangane da maganin da kuma tsinkaya na dalilin ciwo da kuma sauran batutuwa masu gaggawa.
CoVs an san su da cutar da ba ta kashe mutane ba, kuma suna haifar da kusan kashi 15% na cutar 4.
Duk da haka, a wannan ƙarni, mun sami manyan cututtukan CoVs na mutum sau biyu, kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da annoba a China a 2003 da Saudiyya a 2012, bi da bi, wanda ya bazu cikin sauri zuwa wasu ƙasashe tare da rashin lafiya mai tsanani da mutuwa.
