Coronaviruses (CoVs) na cikin iyalin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi ƙungiyoyi masu haɗuwa, masu nuna alama, ƙwayoyin RNA guda ɗaya.
Wadannan ƙwayoyin cuta suna da babban asalin kwayoyin cuta na 26 zuwa 32 kilobases na RNA wanda ake kira "CoV" saboda ƙwayoyin halitta na kwayoyin halitta idan aka duba su a ƙaramin microscope.
A tsarin, CoVs suna da tsarin halittu wanda ba a rarraba shi ba don su kasance cikin ƙungiya ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta na DNA sun ƙunshi manyan kwayoyin guda biyu masu karanta saƙonni (ORF1a da ORF1b), wanda aka fassara zuwa pp1a da pp1b replicase polyprotein.
An sake amfani da polyprotein don samar da furotin 16 marasa tsari, wanda aka tsara a nsp1 ~ 16.
Sauran kwayoyin halitta na kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi ORF yo don tsarin furotin, ciki har da spikes (s), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
An sanya wasu furotin na musamman a cikin jerin inda CoVs suka ɓace a wurare daban-daban.
Dangane da bambancin tsarin furotin, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa rukuni huɗu (alpha-CoV, bet-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), wanda rukuni na bet-CoV ya ƙunshi yawancin HCoVs kuma an rarraba su zuwa nau'ikan farko huɗu (A, B, C da D).
