A wannan rana, USNS Comfort, wani asibiti mai asibiti mai kusan gado 1000, ya rufe a New York.
A ranar 3 ga watan Afrilu, Amurka ta yi rikodin mutuwar mutane 884 sakamakon cutar coronavirus a cikin awanni 24.
A jihar New York, adadin mutane sun wuce 100,000 a ranar 3 ga Afrilu. An soki Fadar White House saboda rage haɗari da kuma sarrafa saƙonni ta hanyar ba da umarnin hukumomin lafiya da masana kimiyya su haɗa labarai da wallafe-wallafen da suka shafi cutar a ofishin mataimakin shugaban Amurka Mike Pence.
Ana nuna rashin amincewa da gwamnatin Trump game da annobar a tsakanin masu raba gardama.
Wasu shugabannin Amurka da masu sharhi sun soki amincewar Amurka da muhimmancin da ta ba da ga kayayyakin kiwon lafiya masu mahimmanci, ciki har da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya na asali, da aka shigo da su daga China.
An yi amfani da tsarin tafiye-tafiye na iska don yin hoto da hango ko hasashen yanayin yaduwar kuma an buga shi a cikin Journal of Travel Medicine a tsakiyar Janairu 202o.
A cewar bayanan 2018 na kungiyar jiragen sama ta kasa da kasa, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, da Taipei sun sami mafi yawan masu tashi daga Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney, da Melbourne kuma an ruwaito cewa sune wuraren da aka fi ziyarta daga Wuhan zuwa Wuhan.
An ruwaito cewa Bali ita ce mafi ƙarancin shirye-shirye daga cikin manyan biranen 20 da masu yawon buɗe ido ke tafiya zuwa, yayin da aka gano manyan biranen Ostiraliya a matsayin mafi shirye-shirye. Ostiraliya ta saki Shirin Amsa na gaggawa ga sabon kwayar cutar Corona (COVID-19) a ranar 7 ga Fabrairu.
An ce har yanzu ba a san komai game da COVID-19 ba, kuma Ostiraliya za ta mai da hankali kan kula da iyakoki da sadarwa don amsa cutar ta duniya.
A ranar 21 ga Maris, an sanar da matakan kare dan Adam daga abubuwa masu haɗari a Ostiraliya.
Tare da ingantaccen keɓewa na jigilar jama'a a Wuhan da Hubei, ƙasashe da yawa sun shirya ƙaurawar jama'arsu da ayyukan sufuri daga wurin, da farko ta hanyar amfani da jiragen haya na ƙasar, tare da ba mu izinin zama na yau da kullun daga shugabannin China.
Kanada, Amurka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransa, Argentina, Jatmalka, da Thailand sun kasance daga cikin na farko da suka yi dariya game da ambaliyar gidaje ga mazauninsu.
Pakistan ta ce ba za ta fitar da wani daga kasar Sin ba.
A ranar 7 ga watan Fabrairu, Brazil ta yi ambaliyar ruwa da mutane 34 na Brazil ko 'yan uwa ban da hudu na Poland, Sin, da Indiya.
An dawo da 'yan asalin Poland, China, da Indiya zuwa Poland, lokacin da jirgin saman Brazil ya tsaya a tsakiyar kafin ya ci gaba da tafiya zuwa Brazil.
An killace wani ɗan ƙasar Brazil da ya tafi Wuhan a wani sansanin soja kusa da Brasília.
A wannan ranar, an kwashe masu tono 215 daga Kanada (176 tare da jirgin sama na farko, da mutane 39 tare da jirgin sama na biyu da gwamnatin Amurka ta haya) daga Wuhan kuma an kai su CFB Trenton don keɓewa na makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama kamar na Kanada 185 daga Wuhan ya sauka a kan jirgin CFB Trenton.
Hukumomin Ostiraliya sun yiwa 'yan kasar 277 albarka a ranar 3 da 4 ga Fabrairu a Cibiyar Kurkuku ta Tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka sanya a matsayin wuri na keɓewa, inda suka zauna na kwanaki 14.
Jirgin saman da ya tashi daga New Zealand ya isa Auckland a ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, kuma an killace fasinjojinsa (ciki har da waɗanda suka fito daga Ostiraliya da Pacific) a wani tashar sojin ruwa a Whanaparoa, arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta tura jami'an Amurka zuwa jirgin ruwa mai suna Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, jirgin sama mai dauke da fasinjoji 129 na Kanada daga Diamond Princess ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara fitar da 'yan kasar ta daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga Maris, jirgin saman South African Airways na gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ya dawo da 'yan kasar 112 daga Afirka ta Kudu.
An gudanar da bincike na asibiti kafin a kai hari, kuma an bar Afirka ta Kudu 4 da suka nuna alamun cutar coronavirus don rage haɗarin.
Sai dai mutanen Afirka ta Kudu da suka bace ne aka mayar da su kasar.
Sakamakon binciken ya bayyana cewa duk mutanen Afirka ta Kudu, gami da ma'aikatan jirgin sama, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal, 'yan sanda da sojoji da ke da hannu a ayyukan jin kai, an kiyaye su duka a cikin killacewa na kwanaki 14 a Ranch Resort.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye sojojinta daga Iraki saboda tashin hankali.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin ta ce kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar, da Iran) sun aika da taimako ga kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin daga jami'o'in Amurka sun taru don taimakawa wajen tura sassan da cutar ta addabi kasar Sin, tare da wata kungiya mai haɗawa a babban yankin Chicago da aka ruwaito ta gudanar da aikawa da masks N95 50,000 zuwa asibitin yankin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu. Ta hanyar taimakon kai tsaye na Cibiyar Taimako ga Jama'a, wanda ke aiki tare da FEDEX, an aika da masks na fuska 200,000 tare da wasu kayan kariya na mutum, gami da gashin hannu da gashin ciki, tare da jigilar gaggawa zuwa asibitin Wuhan Union a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da kyautar sadaka na dala miliyan 100 daga WHO don tallafawa gwajin allurar rigakafi da ƙoƙarin magani yayin kare "mutanen da ke cikin haɗari a Afirka da Asiya".
Kamfanin Interaksyon ya ruwaito cewa gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ba da masks 200,000 ga Filipinos a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan da masanin fasaha Richard Gordon ya ba da masks miliyan 3.16 ga Wuhan.
A ranar 9 ga watan Fabrairu, Kamfanin Red Sea na Singapore ya sanar da cewa zai aika da tallafin dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da masks miliyan daya a Wuhan, Turkiyya ta ba da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da kayan aikin kiwon lafiya sama da tan 13 zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta ba da kyautar kayan aikin kiwon lafiya miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayan kiwon lafiya daban-daban ga marasa lafiya 10,000 na Hazmat, kuma Amurka ta ba da tan 17.8 na kayan kiwon lafiya ga China kuma ta yi alkawarin ƙarin dala miliyan 100 don tallafawa ƙasashen da cutar ta shafa. Bayan da ya bayyana cewa China ta sami ƙaruwa, ƙasar ta aika da taimako ga ƙasashe daban-daban da cutar ta shafa a duniya.
A tsakiyar Marisob, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayan aikin likita da masana don taimakawa Italiya wajen magance mummunan cutar coronavirus.
Jack Ma ya aika da kayan bincike miliyan 1.1, abin rufe fuska miliyan 6, da kuma kayan kariya 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha don rarraba wa Kungiyar Afirka.
Daga nan ya aika da kayan bincike 5,000, masks 100,000 da kuma masu ba da numfashi 5 zuwa Panama.
Shin ya kuma ba da kayan aikin kiwon lafiya ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkiyya, Georgia, da Jamhuriyar Czech sun bayyana damuwarsu game da masks da kayan aikin bincike da China ta yi.
Misali, Spain ta cire kayan gwajin coronavirus 58,000 na kasar Sin da ke da daidaito na kashi 30%, a lokaci guda kuma, Netherlands ta dawo da masks na fuska 600,000 na kasar Sin wadanda ba su da kyau.
Belgium ta dawo da masks 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, wanda ake zaton sun fito ne daga China, amma a zahiri daga Colombia.
A bangaren Latin Amurka da Afirka, an yi maraba da taimakon da kasar Sin ke bayarwa. A ranar 2 ga Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya fara ba da tallafi mai sauri ga kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar ta WHO ta yaba da kokarin da hukumomin kasar Sin ke yi na sarrafa da kuma hana ambaliyar.
Hukumar ta WHO ta ce ta yi adawa da barkewar cutar SARS tsakanin 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da ɓoye jinkirin hanawa da kuma hanawa, da kuma annobar yanzu yayin da gwamnatin tsakiya "ta samar da sabon tsari don hana tashin hankali a hutun Sabuwar Shekarar Lunar".
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a cikin martani ga shawarar da hukumomin tsakiya suka yanke game da dokar hana zirga-zirgar Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya lura cewa ba "shawarwarin WHO ba ne", shi ma "babban mahimmin abin da ke tattare da ƙaddamar da rigakafin a wuraren da ya fi yawa" kuma ya kira shi "ba a tabbatar da tarihin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, yayin da wakilin WHO ya tabbatar da cewa yana ci gaba da ƙaruwa ga bil'adama a cikin kasar Sin da kuma ƙaruwar yawan shari'o'in a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta sanar da cewa an yi gaggawa a cikin gaggawa a cikin allurar rigakafin Lafiya ta Jama'a (PHEIC), har zuwa na shida na PHEIC da aka yi a cikin jerin sunayen a shekarar 2009.
Babban daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce PHEIC tana da "hadarin yaduwar duniya, musamman a ƙasashen da ke da ƙananan da matsakaitan kuɗi waɗanda ba su da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya.
A cikin martani ga matakan hana zirga-zirga, Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili da zai sa ba a yi aiki da kyau tare da zirga-zirga da kasuwancin duniya ba" kuma "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar hana zirga-zirga da kasuwanci".
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta nemi taimakon dala miliyan 675 daga al'ummar duniya don tallafawa shirye-shiryen dabarun ƙasashe masu ƙananan kuɗi, yana nuna gaggawa don tallafawa waɗannan ƙasashe "ba su da tsarin gano mutane da suka kamu da cutar, koda kuwa ta bayyana".
Tedros ya kara da cewa a cikin labarin "mun fi karfi ne kawai a matsayin mu na rashin dangantaka" kuma ya yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su "yi zuba jari a yau ko kuma su biya fiye da haka gobe". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta kira cutar COVID-1 a taron manema labarai.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya ce Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Antonio Guterres ya amince ya ba da "hakki ga tsarin aikin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya".
An tura kungiyar kula da bala'in Majalisar Dinkin Duniya saboda sakamakon, ta ba da izinin haɗin kai a cikin ayyukan da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ke yi, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba ta damar "daidaita hankali kan aikin lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya ba da ƙwarewa don magance tasirin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki da ci gaban cutar".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an kafa Ƙungiyar Aiki ta WHO da ke jagorantar Sin don tabbatar da cewa masana na duniya da na WHO a China suna taimakawa wajen gudanar da ayyukan gida da kimanta "ciwo da yaduwar cutar" ta hanyar gudanar da tarurruka da tarurruka tare da mahimman abubuwan da ke tattare da cutar a matakin ƙasa da kuma yin ziyara a wurin don kimanta "samar da ayyukan amsawa a matakin yanki da na gwamnati, gami da birane da yankunan karkara". A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta ba da sanarwar cewa "ta yi abubuwa da yawa don kasancewa a kan gaba wajen magance yiwuwar cutar coronavirus a duniya", duk da cewa a wani lokaci ana bukatar "tabbata ta duniya".
A sakamakon ci gaba da kisan kai a Iran, WHO ta aika da Ƙungiyar Aiki ta Ƙungiya don tantance halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce ana haɓaka kimantawar haɗarin coronavirus a duniya daga "babba" zuwa "mafi girma", tare da mafi girman matakin gargadi da kimanta haɗari.
Mike Ryan, darektan gudanarwa na shirin kiwon lafiya na gaggawa na WHO, ya yi gargadin a cikin wata kasida cewa "Wannan tabbaci ne na gaskiya ga kowane gwamnati a duniya: Toosa,
Wannan kwayar cutar na iya kasancewa a hanya kuma kuna buƙatar kasancewa a shirye", in ji shi, yana mai cewa matakan da suka dace na iya taimakawa duniya ta guje wa "mafi munin".
Ryan ya kara da cewa bayanan yanzu ba su tabbatar da cewa hukumomin kiwon lafiya na jama'a za su ayyana cutar a duniya ba, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwar tana nufin "mun yarda da cewa kowane ɗan adam a duniya yana kamuwa da cutar.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, WHO ta ayyana cutar coronavirus a matsayin cuta ta duniya.
Babban daraktan WHO ya ce WHO "ta damu sosai game da mummunan matakin yaduwar cutar da tashin hankali, da kuma mummunan matakin rashin aikin yi". WHO ta fuskanci mummunan zargi game da abin da ke da alama bai isa ya magance cutar ta duniya ba, ciki har da jinkirin sanar da dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya ta jama'a da kuma gane cutar a matsayin cutar ta duniya.
A cikin zargi an haɗa da takardar neman izinin shugaban hukumar WHO Tedros Adhanom ya yi murabus, wanda mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a ranar 6 ga Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, wani binciken da masana kare hakkin bil'adama na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya suka yi ya sake tabbatar da girmama hakkin kowa a lokacin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar masana ta ce kowa yana da hakkin ya yi aikin ceto rai kuma gwamnati ce ke da alhakin hakan.
Wasu kungiyoyi sun jaddada cewa rashin samun kudin shiga ko inshorar lafiya ba zai taba zama hujja ba ga nuna bambanci ga wani rukuni.
Masana sun jaddada cewa kowa yana da hakkin samun lafiya, ciki har da nakasassu, daga ƙananan kungiyoyi, manya, 'yan gudun hijira, marasa gida, waɗanda ke rayuwa a cikin yanayi mai wuya, waɗanda ke kurkuku, da kuma 'yan gudun hijira da sauran kungiyoyin da ba a bayyana su ba waɗanda ke bukatar tallafin gwamnati.
Hukumomin gwamnati na duniya sun yi rahoton tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar hadin gwiwar tattalin arziki da ci gaba ta kaddamar da wani dandamali wanda zai samar da cikakken bayani a kan yadda kasashen duniya ke amsawa, da kuma ra'ayoyi da shawarwari.
Daga hanyoyin karfafa tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arzikin duniya zuwa tattauna tasirin hanawa da takunkumin balaguro, cibiyar zamani, ciki har da Cibiyar Kula da Dokokin Kasa, tana nufin taimaka wa ƙasashe su koya da sauƙaƙe haɗin gwiwar duniya game da ƙalubalen coronavirus.
Gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi Allah wadai da Amurka, Ministan ministocin Birtaniya Michael Gove, da kuma dan shugaban kasar Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, kan yadda suka magance annobar da ta bullo a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
An kara yawan hukumomin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin a matakin larduna kan yadda suka bi da kokarin killace jama'a a kasar Sin ta tsakiya, a matsayin alamar rashin gamsuwa da yadda siyasa ke mayar da martani ga rashin nutsuwa a wadannan yankuna.
Masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa wannan matakin zai kare babban sakataren jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin Xi Jinping daga tserewa daga cutar coronavirus.
Wasu jami'an kasar Sin, misali Zhao Lijian sun musanta yarda da farko cewa cutar coronavirus ta fara ne a Wuhan, suna la'akari da ra'ayoyin makirci game da COVID-19 ko ta fito ne daga Amurka ko Italiya.
Gwamnatin Amurka Donald Trump ta bayyana coronavirus a matsayin "virus na kasar Sin" ko "virus na Wuhan" inda ta ce binciken da kasar Sin ta yi ya haifar da cutar da ta zama annoba ta duniya", wanda masu sukar ta yi la'akari da ita a matsayin launin ƙiyayya da kuma nuna wa mutane yadda gwamnatinsa ta gaza wajen sarrafa cutar".
Jaridar Daily Beast ta gano wani rahoto na gwamnatin Amurka da ke nuna magudi a harkokin sadarwa da ke da asalinsa a Majalisar Tsaro ta Kasa, tare da dabarun da ke cewa "Dukkanin game da China ne.
An gaya mana mu yi kokarin samun wadannan sakonni ta duk hanyar da za mu iya, ciki har da taron manema labarai da kuma hotunan talabijin. "Shafukan labarai kamar Politico, Siyasa ta waje, da Bloomberg sun ce kokarin da kasar Sin ke yi na tura tallafi ga kasashen da cutar ta shafa na daga cikin matsin lamba ga duniya.
Shugaban siyasar kasashen waje na EU Josep Borrell ya yi gargadin cewa akwai "rashin daidaituwa a cikin siyasa ta ƙasa wanda ya haɗa da rikice-rikice da ake shafar ta ta hanyar lalata da 'rashin daidaituwa na siyasa'.
Borrell ya kuma ce "China tana tura sakon da karfi, banda Amurka, cewa ita abokiyar da za a iya amincewa da ita".
Kasar Sin ta kuma bukaci Amurka ta cire tallafi daga Syria da Venezuela da Iran, ta tura tallafi ga kasashen biyu na baya.
An dakatar da horon Jack Ma na sanya masks 100,000 a Cuba a ranar 3 ga Afrilu ta Amurka.
An kuma zargi hukumomin Amurka da karkatar da tallafin da ake ba wa wasu kasashe a kasarsu.
An bayar da rahoton cewa akwai matsala game da rufe fuska tsakanin wasu ƙasashe, kamar Jamus, Austria, da Switzerland; da Jamhuriyar Czech da Italiya.
Bugu da kari, Turkiyya ta kama daruruwan injunan numfashi da aka tura zuwa Spain.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta yi Allah wadai da rashin kulawar da kungiyar Tarayyar Turai ke yi wa Italiya game da cutar coronavirus.
Jakadan Italiya a EU, Maurizio Massari, ya ce "China ce kawai ta amsa da bambanci.
Wannan ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga daidaiton Turai".
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, bayan kiran waya da Firayim Ministan Italiya Giuseppe Conte, Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya shirya tura sojojin Rasha likitocin soji, motocin kashe-kashe na musamman, da sauran kayan aikin kiwon lafiya zuwa Italiya.
Jaridar Italiya Stampa ta nakalto "mafi kyawun tushen siyasa" wanda ba a san shi ba cewa kashi 80 cikin dari na tallafin Rasha "ba shi da amfani ko kuma ba shi da amfani ga Italiya".
Majiyar ta zargi Rasha da kafa "dandalin siyasa da diflomasiyya" don tallafawa bincike.
Shugaban Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, da Ministan Harkokin Wajen Italiya Luigi Di Maio sun janye rahoton kafofin watsa labarai kuma sun nuna godiyarsu.
Rasha ta kuma tura jirgin sama mai dauke da kaya zuwa Amurka don kai taimakon kiwon lafiya.
Kakakin Kremlin Dmitry Peskov ya ce "a lokacin da ake ba da tallafi ga abokan Amurka, [Putin] ya ɗauka cewa lokacin da masana'antun kayan aikin kiwon lafiya da sauran kayan aikin Amurka suka sami iko, za su iya ba da lada idan ya cancanta".
Za a gudanar da shirin shirin NATO na soja na "Defense 2020" a Jamus, Poland, da kasashen Baltic, wanda shi ne babban taron NATO tun bayan karshen yakin sanyi, a wani karamin matakin.
Sakatare Janar na Hukumar Sanya Makaman Nukiliya Kate Hudsan ta soki shirin kare dakarun kasar na shekarar 2020: "Abubuwan da ke damun lafiyar jama'a a yanzu, suna barazana ga rayukan ba kawai sojojin Amurka da kasashen Turai da dama ba, har ma da mazauna kasashen da suke aiki". Gwamnatin Iran ta sha wahala sosai daga cutar, tare da kusan 'yan majalisa goma sha biyu da kuma wasu 'yan siyasa goma sha biyar da ke da alhakin siyasa a yanzu ko a baya.
Shugaban Iran Hassan Rouhani ya rubuta wata wasika ta musamman ga shugabannin duniya yana neman taimako a ranar 14 ga Maris, 2020, yana mai cewa kasarsa ta gaji da fama da rashin amincewa da kasuwannin duniya sakamakon rashin tallafin da Amurka ta yi wa Iran. Fitar da annobar ta haifar da kira ga Amurka ta aiwatar da hanyoyin da suka fi sauran ƙasashe adalci, gami da kula da lafiya ta duniya, kula da yara na duniya, hutun iyali mai albashi, da kuma babban matakin kudaden kiwon lafiyar jama'a.
Masu nazarin siyasa sun yi hasashen cewa hakan zai shafi yiwuwar sake zaben Donald Trump a zaben shugaban kasa na 2020. Dangantakar diflomasiyya tsakanin Japan da Koriya ta Kudu ta kara tabarbarewa sakamakon annobar duniya.
Koriya ta Kudu ta yi suka kan "saurin yin keɓewa" bayan da Japan ta sanar da cewa za a yi wa duk wanda ya zo daga Koriya ta Kudu keɓewa na makonni biyu a wuraren da gwamnati ta shirya.
A Koriya ta Kudu, al'umma sun riga sun raba game da yadda Shugaba Moon Jae-in ya amsa bala'in.
Yawancin 'yan Koriya sun sanya hannu kan takardar neman cewa za a tsige Moon saboda abin da suka ce game da rashin adalci na gwamnati a cikin barkewar cutar, ko kuma don yaba da martani. Cutar ta duniya ta ba wa ƙasashe damar aiwatar da dokar ta baci don amsawa.
Wasu manazarta sun nuna damuwa cewa hakan zai ba gwamnatoci damar karfafa ikon su.
A Hungary, majalisa ta kada kuri'a don ba da izinin mai lalata, Viktor Orban, ya gabatar da doka ba tare da nuna bambanci ba, ya dakatar da majalisa da kuma zaɓen kuma ya hukunta waɗanda aka ɗauka suna yada bayanan karya game da cutar da yadda gwamnati ke magance annobar.
An zargi yaduwar cutar korona da karancin wadata a yanayi da dama, wanda ya haifar da karuwar amfani da kayan aiki don yaki da zalunci, sayayya saboda tsoro, da matsalar masana'antu da ayyukan samarwa.
Hukumar Abinci da Magunguna ta Amurka ta ba da gargadi game da raguwar magunguna da kayan aikin kiwon lafiya saboda karuwar bukatar masu amfani da kuma rashin wadatar masu samar da kayayyaki.
