ACE2 yana hana aikin da ke tattare da enzyme mai canza angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang (1-7) wanda ke haifar da magani mai kyau wanda ke niyya ga ciwon zuciya. ACE2 kuma shine hanyar shiga wasu ƙwayoyin cutar coronavirus.
Kwafin enzyme wanda ba na mutum ba ne aka fi sani da hACE2.
Angiostensin-reversible enzyme 2 shine sinadarin da ke cikin metalloenzyme a cikin endothelial surface da sauran sel.
Protein ACE2 yana dauke da N-terminal na peptidase M2 na yankin da kuma C-terminal wanda ke dauke da yankin amino acid.
ACE2 shine kawai nau'in furotin I, wanda ke da wani yanki mai aiki na enzymatic wanda ke kaiwa saman ƙwayoyin huhu da sauran ƙwayoyin.
Ƙarin ƙwayoyin halitta na ACE2 suna ƙunshe da ƙwayoyin halitta waɗanda ke ɗaukar enzyme mai suna sheddase, wanda ke samar da furotin mai narkewa wanda ke shiga cikin jijiyoyin jini kuma yana lalata abubuwan da aka samar a cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin ƙwayoyin halitta: ACE2 yana kai hari ga ƙwayoyin halitta na yau da kullum a cikin huhu na alveolar cell type II, enterocytes a cikin ƙananan hanji, ƙwayoyin jijiya da endothelial da ƙwayoyin tsoka na ƙwayoyin halitta.
Hakanan ana samun ACE2mRNA mai ƙididdiga a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa, striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma ƙwayoyin kwakwalwa.
Aikin farko na ACE2 shine daidaita ACE.
Kwayoyin ACE suna rarraba angiotensin I a cikin ƙwayar angiotensin II.
ACE2 yana karɓar carboxyl-terminal acid phenylalanine angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyrlle-His-Pro-Phe) da hydrolyses kuma yana sanya su cikin vasodalitor angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyrlle-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 yana karɓar wasu nau'ikan peptides ciki har da [des-arg9] - bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A da ghrelin.
Hakanan ACE2 yana sarrafa tsarin amino acid mai tsaka tsaki wanda aka samo daga SLC6A19 wanda aka bayyana a cikin cutar Hartnup.
A cikin furotin na motsi na ƙwayar cuta, ACE2 shine babban hanyar shiga kwayar cutar coronavirus, ciki har da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, haɗuwa da haɓakar S1 botorians na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 a cikin yankin enzymatic na ACE2 a saman sel daga endocytosis da watsa kwayar cutar da kuma enzyme na yaduwa a cikin endosomes a cikin sel.
Duk wannan tsarin yana buƙatar haɓaka ƙwayoyin cuta na S na TMPRSS2, wanda aka cire daga hanci wanda a halin yanzu ana bincika shi a matsayin furotin na halitta. Wannan na iya haifar da zato cewa zai iya rage matakan ACE2, a cikin tantanin halitta, wanda zai iya taimakawa wajen magance ciwo.
Amma, al'ummomin sana'a da yawa da kungiyoyin da suka kafa dokoki sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da yawan shan ACE da ARB.
Wani bincike na yau da kullum da kuma kimantawa na ƙarfe da aka fitar a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, ya gano cewa "amfani da numfashi na ACE yana da alaƙa da raguwa mai girma na 34% na haɗarin ciwon huhu fiye da yadda aka sarrafa shi".
Haka kuma, "hadarin ciwon huhu na iya ragewa ga marasa lafiya da ke shan maganin numfashi na ACE wanda hakan ke haifar da haɗarin ciwo, musamman ga mutanen da ke fama da ciwon hanci da zuciya.
Yin amfani da maganin numfashi na ACE wanda ke da alaƙa da cututtukan huhu na mutuwa yana rage, kodayake maganin numfashi ba shi da tasiri sosai idan aka kwatanta da haɗarin cututtukan huhu gaba ɗaya".
Haɗuwa zuwa mutum na ACE2 (rhACE2) wanda shine babban magani na sabon magani na mummunan rauni na huhu, da kuma ci gaba a cikin haemodynamics na ƙwayoyin cuta da oxygen mai yawa a cikin alade tare da alamun ciwon numfashi mai tsanani tare da lipopolysaccharide.
Rayuwar rabi na rhACE2 ba tare da mutum ba ya kai sa'o'i 10 kuma bisa ga aikin, an ƙara minti 30 zuwa tsawon sa'o'i 24.
Yawancin karatu sun nuna cewa rhACE2 magani ne mai amfani ga mutanen da ba za su iya shan maganin numfashi mai suna renin-angiotesin (RAS) ba ko kuma cutar da ke tattare da angiotensin II ta ƙaru. An kimanta amfani da rhACE2 a cikin gwaji na asibiti don magance cututtukan numfashi masu tsanani.
