Binciken da aka yi akan chloroquine da hydroxchloroquine tare da ko ba tare da azithromycin ba ya iyakance ƙuntatawa a cikin al'umma ta kiwon lafiya don gano wannan magani ba tare da yin binciken ba. Oseltamivir ba ya iyakance shan SARS-CoV-2 a cikin vitro kuma ba a san rawar da yake takawa a cikin maganin COVID-19.
Cyroquin hadari na iya zama matsala mai tsanani a ƙarshen COVID-19.
Akwai hujja cewa hydroxychloroquine na iya samun tasirin anti-cytokine. Tocilizumab kuma yana cikin magani a cikin umarnin Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta Jayna bayan kammala binciken.
Idan ba a yi amfani da hanyar 2 ba a matsayin wata hanyar da aka yi amfani da ita a cikin Italiya bayan an gano cewa ta kasance mai kyau ga mutanen da ke fama da ciwo mai tsanani.
Hada ferritin serum da kwayoyin jini don gano cytokine na hadari, yana nufin wani abu da aka yi don yaki da cutar, wanda aka ɗauka yana haifar da mutuwar wasu mutane.
FDA ta amince da mai karɓar interleukin-6 mai karɓar maganin, bisa ga sakamakon binciken likita na abin da ke haifar da isotonin cytokine wanda ke haifar da kumburi, CAR T cell mai lura, a shekara ta 2017.
Har yanzu, babu wata hujja ta hana rigakafin cutar ta CRS.
Ana gudanar da bincike kan samar da maganin rigakafi mai tsafta da kuma karko a tsarin rigakafin mutanen da ke murmurewa daga COVID-19 ga mutanen da ke cikin bukata ta hanyar rigakafin da ba rigakafi ba.
An biya wannan kuɗin don maganin SARS wanda ya haɗa da sakamakon da bai cika ba.
Ana iya watsa kwayar cutar a cikin hanyar da ake so ta maganin maganin hana bacci zuwa SARS-CoV-2.
Amma wasu hanyoyi, kamar maganin rigakafi wanda ya dogara da cytotoxicity a cikin sel da / ko phagocytosis, suna yiwuwa.
Ana yin wasu nau'ikan maganin anti-jump, misali, ta amfani da maganin anti-jump monoclonal.
Abubuwan da ke cikin ƙwayar cuta, wanda ya ƙunshi wani ɓangare na jini daga cikin marasa lafiya wanda ya ƙunshi wani maganin rigakafi na ƙwayoyin cuta, zai iya haɓaka haɓakar sauri.
